(Random Assignment, Detectives, Suspect)
Once a case begins,

22
00:01:08,400 --> 00:01:10,400
players will be randomly
assigned the role

23
00:01:10,400 --> 00:01:11,360
of detectives or suspect.

24
00:01:11,880 --> 00:01:14,160
(Suspect, NPC)
The true culprit may be either one

25
00:01:14,160 --> 00:01:15,520
of the suspect players or an NPC.

26
00:01:15,520 --> 00:01:17,400
(True Culprit)
Judge carefully.

27
00:01:17,400 --> 00:01:19,240
True culprit's objective
is to conceal their identity

28
00:01:19,240 --> 00:01:20,720
and avoid detection.

29
00:01:20,720 --> 00:01:23,400
(True Culprit)
Only the true culprit is allowed to lie.

30
00:01:23,400 --> 00:01:24,000
(Main Quest, Evidence
Collection, Exploration, Rewards)

31
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:24,760
During investigation,

32
00:01:24,760 --> 00:01:25,500
(Skill Cards, Trial,
Stamina Points, Side Quest)

33
00:01:25,500 --> 00:01:27,200
players can progress
the case through various game mechanics.

34
00:01:27,200 --> 00:01:28,800
to further the investigation.

35
00:01:29,480 --> 00:01:30,800
Use these mechanics wisely.

36
00:01:30,800 --> 00:01:32,400
