129
00:04:31,540 --> 00:04:34,940
(260th Year of the Tui Calendar. Fifth
Month, 26th Day, in the late afternoon)

130
00:04:38,220 --> 00:04:39,680
(Door of Truth)

131
00:04:39,680 --> 00:04:40,680
Long ago,

132
00:04:41,080 --> 00:04:42,280
three kingdoms of Tui, Li, and Kuang

133
00:04:42,280 --> 00:04:43,400
stood in a three-way rivalry,

134
00:04:43,400 --> 00:04:44,600
each ruling its own territory.

135
00:04:46,440 --> 00:04:48,360
Why does the Kingdom
of Kuang no longer exist?

136
00:04:49,080 --> 00:04:50,400
In year 254 of Tui,

137
00:04:50,840 --> 00:04:51,920
Kuang Kingdom was destroyed

138
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:52,840
by Tui and Li,

139
00:04:53,480 --> 00:04:54,760
who divided its lands between them.

140
00:04:55,440 --> 00:04:56,640
The story begins in Tui City.

141
00:04:56,640 --> 00:04:57,240
(Tui City)

142
00:04:57,240 --> 00:04:59,080
Located at the crossroads
of several nations,

143
00:04:59,080 --> 00:05:01,720
Tui City is a lawless frontier
where strength rules.

144
00:05:01,720 --> 00:05:03,240
I know of Tui City.

145
00:05:03,240 --> 00:05:05,360
Its ruler, Lord Tui,

146
00:05:05,720 --> 00:05:06,920
is a true master among masters.

147
00:05:07,320 --> 00:05:07,960
That's right.

148
00:05:07,960 --> 00:05:09,400
Under his leadership, Chivalry Manor

149
00:05:09,400 --> 00:05:11,440
has opened its granaries
to ease hunger and help the people.

150
00:05:11,920 --> 00:05:13,120
As long as he remains in power,

151
00:05:13,120 --> 00:05:14,640
no one dares stir up
trouble within his domain.

152
00:05:14,640 --> 00:05:15,940
(Chivalry Manor)

153
00:05:16,600 --> 00:05:18,200
So he's a man of great virtue.

154
00:05:19,000 --> 00:05:19,800
Sadly, peace did not last.

155
00:05:21,040 --> 00:05:23,040
Now, whenever night falls,

156
00:05:23,040 --> 00:05:24,480
ghostly soldiers march

157
00:05:24,480 --> 00:05:25,640
through the streets

158
00:05:25,640 --> 00:05:26,640
of Tui City.

159
00:05:34,880 --> 00:05:36,040
Spectral figures appear one by one,

160
00:05:36,040 --> 00:05:37,360
tormenting the townspeople relentlessly.

161
00:05:38,480 --> 00:05:39,480
How did this happen?

162
00:05:39,480 --> 00:05:40,040
Then...

163
00:05:40,040 --> 00:05:41,040
What about Lord Tui?

164
00:05:41,760 --> 00:05:42,880
Even he is powerless to stop it.

165
00:05:42,880 --> 00:05:43,920
Five years ago,

166
00:05:44,320 --> 00:05:46,040
the once-renowned Longdong
Army of the Kingdom of Tui

167
00:05:46,040 --> 00:05:47,040
suffered a crushing defeat.

168
00:05:47,040 --> 00:05:48,040
Ten thousand cavalrymen

169
00:05:48,040 --> 00:05:49,360
fell on this very battlefield.

170
00:05:51,600 --> 00:05:53,360
Wouldn't that mean
over ten thousand restless spirits?

171
00:05:53,360 --> 00:05:54,040
Exactly.

172
00:05:54,520 --> 00:05:55,560
Who could quell such resentment?

173
00:05:56,920 --> 00:05:57,840
In time,

174
00:05:57,840 --> 00:05:58,960
they became ghostly soldiers

175
00:05:58,960 --> 00:06:00,080
who preyed on the living.

176
00:06:02,200 --> 00:06:03,280
What's even more terrifying...

177
00:06:03,680 --> 00:06:05,720
Lately, they have begun
targeting children.

178
00:06:06,320 --> 00:06:07,840
They devour them whole,

179
00:06:08,280 --> 00:06:09,680
leaving not even a single bone behind.

180
00:06:12,960 --> 00:06:13,880
What's to become of me?

181
00:06:14,840 --> 00:06:16,200
I'm still a child!

182
00:06:18,280 --> 00:06:19,080
Ding,

183
00:06:20,280 --> 00:06:21,080
I'm a fortune teller,

184
00:06:21,080 --> 00:06:22,200
not a fool.

185
00:06:24,080 --> 00:06:25,120
I do have a way

186
00:06:25,120 --> 00:06:26,440
to preserve your life.

187
00:06:28,800 --> 00:06:29,680
Tell me.

188
00:06:31,620 --> 00:06:32,160
(Ghost Stories of Tui City)

189
00:06:32,160 --> 00:06:33,360
This book, Ghost Stories of Tui City,

190
00:06:33,360 --> 00:06:35,000
records everything.

191
00:06:35,600 --> 00:06:36,600
With a simple calculation,

192
00:06:36,600 --> 00:06:37,720
I know you are not
a man of great courage.

193
00:06:38,960 --> 00:06:39,840
This book

194
00:06:39,840 --> 00:06:41,120
originally costs 88 coins.

195
00:06:41,120 --> 00:06:42,760
Now, I have reduced the price.

196
00:06:42,760 --> 00:06:43,600
Can you guess how much it costs?

197
00:06:43,920 --> 00:06:44,360
How much?

198
00:06:45,040 --> 00:06:45,760
Three coins.

199
00:06:47,840 --> 00:06:48,480
Give me all of them.

200
00:06:49,120 --> 00:06:50,240
I want every volume,

201
00:06:50,240 --> 00:06:50,880
the prequel, sequel, side stories,
and all companion editions.

202
00:06:51,240 --> 00:06:51,960
You are a good man.

203
