(Pig)

832
00:26:41,660 --> 00:26:42,240
(Dog)

833
00:26:42,240 --> 00:26:42,880
No.

834
00:26:42,880 --> 00:26:44,080
Arrogant and domineering,

835
00:26:44,080 --> 00:26:44,960
