842
00:26:51,040 --> 00:26:52,160
Bullying others with his power.

843
00:26:53,080 --> 00:26:53,720
There's something here.

844
00:27:03,880 --> 00:27:04,360
Don't laugh.

845
00:27:09,320 --> 00:27:09,840
Monster.

846
00:27:10,600 --> 00:27:11,320
What?

847
00:27:12,130 --> 00:27:13,000
I still remember

848
00:27:13,000 --> 00:27:14,720
on the 30th of May,

849
00:27:14,720 --> 00:27:16,320
