a basket of steaming hot buns.

853
00:27:21,480 --> 00:27:23,960
At that moment, you were my goddess.

854
00:27:23,960 --> 00:27:26,080
But now, you use poison
and scheme against others,

855
00:27:26,080 --> 00:27:27,120
with such a wicked heart.

856
00:27:27,120 --> 00:27:29,120
Jin Thrifty, you are a witch.

857
00:27:29,120 --> 00:27:29,880
A witch!

858
00:27:29,880 --> 00:27:31,160
A witch.

859
00:27:31,880 --> 00:27:34,400
Luckily,
I didn't eat that basket of buns.

860
00:27:34,640 --> 00:27:36,520
Who knows what kind of meat was inside.

861
00:27:37,200 --> 00:27:38,080
Tell me.

862
00:27:38,600 --> 00:27:40,360
Who painted this picture?

863
00:27:40,360 --> 00:27:42,680
Who did you cast your witchcraft on?

864
00:27:42,680 --> 00:27:43,520
And who...

865
00:27:43,520 --> 00:27:44,440
is this child?

866
00:27:44,440 --> 00:27:46,840
After I took over this inn,

867
00:27:47,480 --> 00:27:48,840
