872
00:27:54,560 --> 00:27:55,760
I ate them too.

873
00:27:55,760 --> 00:27:57,040
They hired me
because the buns tasted bad.

874
00:27:57,040 --> 00:27:59,240
When I ate them, they were awful too.

875
00:27:59,240 --> 00:28:00,760
I didn't dare eat them.

876
00:28:00,940 --> 00:28:01,640
