894
00:28:26,580 --> 00:28:28,740
(They ate the buns and vanished)
Then they said

895
00:28:28,760 --> 00:28:30,040
I was an old witch.

896
00:28:30,040 --> 00:28:31,760
That I fed them those buns,

897
00:28:31,760 --> 00:28:32,760
and there was something inside

898
00:28:32,760 --> 00:28:35,080
