908
00:28:51,440 --> 00:28:52,400
The Longdong Army.

909
00:28:52,400 --> 00:28:52,800
That's right.

910
00:28:53,440 --> 00:28:55,240
People have always had a legend

911
00:28:55,240 --> 00:28:57,440
