913
00:28:58,960 --> 00:29:00,760
(After the Longdong Army fell,)
Children have strong yang energy,

914
00:29:00,760 --> 00:29:01,880
(they turned into ghost soldiers)
they were offered to them.

915
00:29:02,960 --> 00:29:04,080
Don't come any closer.

916
00:29:04,600 --> 00:29:06,080
Of course, it's just a legend.

917
00:29:06,080 --> 00:29:06,880
But those children

918
00:29:06,880 --> 00:29:08,440
