920
00:29:10,000 --> 00:29:11,600
Everyone started blaming me.

921
00:29:11,600 --> 00:29:13,520
I'm just a beautiful woman.

922
00:29:13,540 --> 00:29:15,540
(Jin Thrifty had nothing to do
with the children's disappearance)

923
00:29:15,560 --> 00:29:16,000
I see.

924
00:29:16,000 --> 00:29:17,160
Someone framed you.

925
00:29:17,720 --> 00:29:19,120
Who framed you? Who spread the rumors?

926
00:29:20,160 --> 00:29:22,080
The Lord of Tui City
spread rumors about me.

927
00:29:22,080 --> 00:29:23,000
So I wanted to kill him.

928
00:29:23,180 --> 00:29:23,660
(Jin Thrifty's motive)

929
00:29:23,660 --> 00:29:24,140
(Against the Lord of Tui Zhuangzhu:
He was slandered by him,)

930
00:29:24,140 --> 00:29:24,540
(forcing her out of Tui City,
so she wanted revenge.)

931
00:29:24,540 --> 00:29:24,900
(Against Ning Waver: He threatened her
and drove her out of Tui City,)

932
00:29:24,900 --> 00:29:25,300
(so she wanted to kill him to stay.)

933
00:29:25,320 --> 00:29:25,680
Okay.

934
00:29:25,840 --> 00:29:27,400
There's something here.

935
00:29:28,760 --> 00:29:29,760
Inside this jar...

936
00:29:31,100 --> 00:29:33,420
(Theres something here)

937
00:29:33,440 --> 00:29:35,120
There's something.

938
00:29:35,720 --> 00:29:36,480
Two locks.

939
00:29:36,760 --> 00:29:37,440
What's the code?

940
00:29:37,680 --> 00:29:37,880
Come on.

941
00:29:37,880 --> 00:29:38,560
What year is it?

942
00:29:38,560 --> 00:29:40,560
It's the

943
00:29:41,400 --> 00:29:42,560
Year 258 of Tui.

944
00:29:42,560 --> 00:29:45,160
(258, May 30)
Year 258 and 530.

945
00:29:48,120 --> 00:29:48,760
258, I've opened it.

946
00:29:48,760 --> 00:29:49,160
258.

947
00:29:49,160 --> 00:29:50,080
What's this?

948
00:29:50,080 --> 00:29:53,200
0530.

949
00:29:53,200 --> 00:29:53,920
Good, that's right.

950
00:29:54,680 --> 00:29:55,120
Alright.

951
00:29:55,320 --> 00:29:55,720
Are

952
00:29:56,600 --> 00:29:57,560
you ready?

953
00:29:57,980 --> 00:29:58,500
(There's something here)

954
00:30:00,800 --> 00:30:01,880
There's

955
00:30:01,880 --> 00:30:02,760
so much more.

956
00:30:03,840 --> 00:30:04,840
They coveted my beauty,

957
00:30:04,840 --> 00:30:06,080
