959
00:30:08,880 --> 00:30:09,520
Who?

960
00:30:09,520 --> 00:30:11,280
What do you mean?

961
00:30:11,680 --> 00:30:13,680
You have delusions, don't you?

962
00:30:13,680 --> 00:30:14,720
(I'm imagining things)

963
00:30:14,720 --> 00:30:15,760
I imagined it.

964
00:30:15,760 --> 00:30:17,960
Then what do you think is wrong
with these statements?

965
00:30:17,960 --> 00:30:18,640
Alright.

966
00:30:18,640 --> 00:30:19,240
Tell me,

967
00:30:19,240 --> 00:30:20,480
(Show us what you've got)
