968
00:30:21,320 --> 00:30:22,040
Back then,

969
00:30:22,440 --> 00:30:23,560
when my workers

970
00:30:23,560 --> 00:30:24,600
left me,

971
00:30:25,040 --> 00:30:26,040
I never expected

972
00:30:26,040 --> 00:30:28,440
