975
00:30:30,800 --> 00:30:32,640
She applied to be a cook.

976
00:30:32,880 --> 00:30:34,080
But I noticed

977
00:30:34,080 --> 00:30:35,200
she would

978
00:30:35,520 --> 00:30:36,360
