How did you connect those two things?

986
00:30:49,400 --> 00:30:50,560
There's something wrong with her.

987
00:30:50,560 --> 00:30:51,480
She has issues.

988
00:30:51,760 --> 00:30:54,160
She really does seem delusional.

989
00:30:54,160 --> 00:30:55,320
Alright, the second one.

990
00:30:55,320 --> 00:30:55,800
Who is this?

991
00:30:56,200 --> 00:30:57,080
Coveting my beauty.

992
00:30:57,080 --> 00:30:57,880
It was like this.

993
00:30:57,880 --> 00:30:58,720
Ke Stubborn

994
00:30:59,160 --> 00:31:01,840
