He would eat while smiling.

997
00:31:07,240 --> 00:31:09,680
Smiling while secretly watching me.

998
00:31:09,680 --> 00:31:12,240
(I'm not overthinking it)
I thought he must have fallen for me.

999
00:31:13,280 --> 00:31:13,560
No,

1000
00:31:13,560 --> 00:31:14,960
I was eating and thinking.

1001
00:31:14,960 --> 00:31:16,120
These buns taste so bad.

1002
00:31:16,120 --> 00:31:16,680
Who made them?

1003
00:31:16,680 --> 00:31:17,240
Was it her?

1004
00:31:17,760 --> 00:31:18,440
That's all it was.

1005
00:31:18,440 --> 00:31:19,760
I was laughing out of frustration.

1006
00:31:21,480 --> 00:31:22,480
So one visit was enough.

1007
00:31:22,480 --> 00:31:23,840
Why did you keep coming back?

1008
00:31:23,840 --> 00:31:25,060
(Why did Ke Stubborn
keep visiting the inn?)

1009
00:31:25,060 --> 00:31:26,260
