1018
00:31:38,960 --> 00:31:41,800
He must have another motive.

1019
00:31:41,800 --> 00:31:42,920
So that night,

1020
00:31:43,160 --> 00:31:45,160
I secretly watched him.

1021
00:31:45,160 --> 00:31:46,040
You...

1022
00:31:46,600 --> 00:31:48,120
(You're sounding more suspicious)
You watched him sleep

1023
00:31:48,120 --> 00:31:49,240
