1024
00:31:49,240 --> 00:31:51,840
What kind of person are you?

1025
00:31:54,720 --> 00:31:55,520
Observing.

1026
00:31:55,920 --> 00:31:58,920
He kept secretly
drinking my ginseng wine.

1027
00:31:59,640 --> 00:32:02,840
He must have wanted
to make himself stronger,

1028
00:32:02,840 --> 00:32:04,520
get a better physique,

1029
00:32:05,240 --> 00:32:07,640
and then pursue me.

1030
00:32:10,640 --> 00:32:12,480
Your thought process is really
different from normal people's.

1031
00:32:13,280 --> 00:32:14,320
So this is who you are.

1032
00:32:14,320 --> 00:32:16,040
(Why did Ding Pillar
keep drinking the ginseng wine?)

1033
00:32:16,040 --> 00:32:17,120
Then,

1034
00:32:17,120 --> 00:32:19,400
my good friend, Yan Reason,

1035
00:32:19,400 --> 00:32:20,240
told me that recently,

1036
00:32:20,360 --> 00:32:21,520
strange people

1037
00:32:21,520 --> 00:32:23,160
had appeared in our city.

1038
00:32:23,360 --> 00:32:26,720
So, she asked me to keep an eye
out for suspicious people.

1039
00:32:26,720 --> 00:32:27,480
I thought about it.

1040
00:32:27,720 --> 00:32:29,160
The three people in my shop

1041
00:32:29,520 --> 00:32:31,520
