1042
00:32:31,520 --> 00:32:33,670
(With Jin Thrifty asking her friend)
So she came to help me investigate.

1043
00:32:33,680 --> 00:32:35,160
(Yan Reason investigates the three of them)
Let's go to her martial arts school.

1044
00:32:35,760 --> 00:32:36,280
Let's go.

1045
00:32:36,280 --> 00:32:37,280
Let's take a look
at the martial arts school.

1046
00:32:38,080 --> 00:32:38,560
Let's go.

1047
00:32:44,440 --> 00:32:45,520
Be careful, Lady Yan.

1048
00:32:50,800 --> 00:32:51,440
Assassin!

1049
00:32:58,720 --> 00:33:00,120
I didn't expect you
to be all show and no substance.

1050
00:33:01,600 --> 00:33:02,760
Looks like our martial contest
for marriage

1051
00:33:02,760 --> 00:33:04,080
