1052
00:33:04,680 --> 00:33:07,280
You two defeated losers,
get off the stage.

1053
00:33:07,640 --> 00:33:08,440
Come, everyone.

1054
00:33:08,440 --> 00:33:09,040
Please step onto the stage.

1055
00:33:12,120 --> 00:33:13,920
Martial contest for marriage.

1056
00:33:15,320 --> 00:33:16,800
(Side Quest)
A reminder from The Truth Online.

1057
00:33:16,800 --> 00:33:18,280
(Martial Contest for Marriage)
Side quest triggered.

1058
00:33:18,280 --> 00:33:19,880
(Yan Reason, played by Sun Leyan)
Win the martial contest

1059
00:33:19,880 --> 00:33:21,600
