1060
00:33:21,600 --> 00:33:22,920
and you'll get new clues.

1061
00:33:24,800 --> 00:33:25,520
Alright, folks.

1062
00:33:25,520 --> 00:33:27,160
This is a martial arts contest.

1063
00:33:27,160 --> 00:33:30,400
You need to win over Lady Yan
before you can talk to her.

1064
00:33:30,400 --> 00:33:31,840
How do we win her over?

1065
00:33:31,840 --> 00:33:33,040
Hey challenger,

1066
00:33:33,040 --> 00:33:34,210
