1067
00:33:34,210 --> 00:33:35,520
Got any secret tricks up your sleeve?

1068
00:33:35,520 --> 00:33:37,360
I've been traveling the world
for over a decade,

1069
00:33:37,360 --> 00:33:39,280
and my main trait
is being budget-conscious.

1070
00:33:39,280 --> 00:33:39,960
When I'm out and about,

1071
00:33:39,960 --> 00:33:41,720
I rely on the Tongcheng Travel app.

1072
00:33:41,720 --> 00:33:43,440
There are discounts
every month on the 17th.

1073
00:33:43,440 --> 00:33:44,480
Up to 70% off on top hotels

1074
00:33:44,480 --> 00:33:45,680
