1075
00:33:45,680 --> 00:33:46,980
I get everything done in one stop.

1076
00:33:47,000 --> 00:33:48,400
Saves the hassle and saves the cash.

1077
00:33:48,400 --> 00:33:50,200
As they say, travel is pricey,

1078
00:33:50,200 --> 00:33:52,400
