are an absolute lifesaver.

1079
00:33:52,400 --> 00:33:54,520
Seems like Tongcheng
is a winner for saving money.

1080
00:33:54,520 --> 00:33:56,360
Whether it's dining, lodging, or travel,

1081
00:33:56,360 --> 00:33:57,240
Tongcheng has everything.

1082
00:33:57,240 --> 00:33:57,920
Exactly.

1083
00:33:57,920 --> 00:34:00,440
Spend your money where it counts.

1084
00:34:00,920 --> 00:34:02,120
Being thrifty is a great skill,

1085
00:34:02,120 --> 00:34:04,280
