1087
00:34:06,080 --> 00:34:06,640
What do you say?

1088
00:34:06,640 --> 00:34:07,760
Do you want to challenge me?

1089
00:34:07,760 --> 00:34:08,840
Game on.

1090
00:34:08,840 --> 00:34:10,400
Bring it. What are we doing?

1091
00:34:10,400 --> 00:34:11,520
It's super simple.

1092
00:34:11,880 --> 00:34:14,520
Let's test your leg techniques,

1093
00:34:14,520 --> 00:34:15,320
