1094
00:34:15,460 --> 00:34:16,630
(Side Quest: Martial Arts Contest
Challenge: Splits)

1095
00:34:16,630 --> 00:34:18,440
Who stretches the furthest?

1096
00:34:18,440 --> 00:34:19,000
It's simple.

1097
00:34:19,000 --> 00:34:20,230
One foot stays behind the red line,

1098
00:34:20,230 --> 00:34:21,800
and you stretch the other foot out.

1099
00:34:22,440 --> 00:34:25,480
Make sure that other foot
reaches this line.

1100
00:34:27,120 --> 00:34:28,920
I worked way too hard last night.

1101
00:34:28,920 --> 00:34:30,150
(Wiped out from an all-nighter)
I can't really do this.

1102
00:34:30,710 --> 00:34:31,080
How about this?

1103
00:34:31,080 --> 00:34:32,150
(He Ha gives up the contest)

1104
00:34:32,150 --> 00:34:33,230
Let Ke Stubborn try first.

1105
00:34:33,230 --> 00:34:33,840
Try first.

1106
00:34:33,840 --> 00:34:34,000
Me?

1107
00:34:35,150 --> 00:34:36,000
Just do your best.

1108
00:34:41,120 --> 00:34:43,150
Ke Stubborn is a bit stiff.

1109
00:34:43,180 --> 00:34:45,660
(Ultimate stiff guy)

1110
00:34:45,670 --> 00:34:46,190
I can't.

1111
00:34:46,190 --> 00:34:47,080
I'm about to cramp up.

1112
00:34:47,520 --> 00:34:48,280
Alright, next.

1113
00:34:48,840 --> 00:34:50,040
We have to do this either way.

1114
00:34:53,600 --> 00:34:54,480
You got this.

1115
00:34:54,800 --> 00:34:55,230
Yeah.

1116
00:34:55,230 --> 00:34:55,880
He's flexible.

1117
00:34:55,880 --> 00:34:56,920
He's got a background in dance.

1118
00:34:58,720 --> 00:34:59,480
You got this.

1119
00:35:02,940 --> 00:35:05,260
(Argh)

1120
00:35:06,680 --> 00:35:07,360
That's your limit.

1121
00:35:07,360 --> 00:35:08,120
Don't push it too hard.

1122
00:35:08,560 --> 00:35:09,680
I can't reach it.

1123
00:35:10,360 --> 00:35:11,080
I can't go any lower.

1124
00:35:11,720 --> 00:35:12,320
I'm done.

1125
00:35:12,720 --> 00:35:13,800
It hurts so bad.

1126
00:35:14,700 --> 00:35:15,820
(Three consecutive losses)

1127
00:35:15,840 --> 00:35:16,800
Ning Waver.

1128
00:35:28,360 --> 00:35:29,640
Word has it that this man

1129
00:35:29,640 --> 00:35:31,160
has the best agility.

1130
00:35:31,160 --> 00:35:31,920
That's right.

1131
00:35:31,920 --> 00:35:34,120
The ultimate legs
of the martial arts world?

1132
00:35:34,120 --> 00:35:34,960
(The ultimate legs)
That would be me.

1133
00:35:35,160 --> 00:35:38,240
Why do I feel like
I'm about to become the groom?

1134
00:35:41,520 --> 00:35:42,320
Go forward a little more.

1135
00:35:50,100 --> 00:35:53,100
(The ultimate legs)

1136
00:35:53,560 --> 00:35:55,000
How did you do that? You're amazing.

1137
00:35:55,000 --> 00:35:55,920
You can actually do the splits.

1138
00:35:55,920 --> 00:35:56,720
Impressive.

1139
00:35:56,720 --> 00:35:58,680
Why would you even
practice this kind of stuff?

1140
00:35:58,680 --> 00:36:00,120
Are you a yoga fan?

1141
00:36:00,120 --> 00:36:00,960
You practice at home every day?

1142
00:36:00,960 --> 00:36:01,600
That's right.

1143
00:36:02,600 --> 00:36:03,200
For my health.

1144
00:36:03,760 --> 00:36:06,040
Even if I do a full split,
I still won't reach it.

1145
00:36:07,680 --> 00:36:08,720
Go a bit further.

1146
00:36:08,720 --> 00:36:09,960
Almost there.

1147
00:36:10,920 --> 00:36:11,520
I think

1148
00:36:11,840 --> 00:36:14,160
we have two winners now.

1149
00:36:14,880 --> 00:36:16,920
(Affinity with locals +1)
You two can make any request.

1150
00:36:16,920 --> 00:36:18,000
I don't really have a wish.

1151
00:36:18,000 --> 00:36:20,520
I just want to know
what you can give us.

1152
00:36:22,240 --> 00:36:24,840
I do have what you want.

1153
00:36:25,200 --> 00:36:27,080
And I've run a check.

1154
00:36:27,480 --> 00:36:29,240
You aren't the troublemakers.

1155
00:36:29,640 --> 00:36:30,920
Cui Geng, bring the things out.

1156
00:36:31,520 --> 00:36:32,280
Here, everyone.

1157
00:36:33,080 --> 00:36:33,360
Alright.

1158
00:36:33,720 --> 00:36:35,480
So these are the things
you can give us, right?

1159
00:36:35,480 --> 00:36:37,600
They have corresponding names on them.

1160
00:36:37,600 --> 00:36:38,520
To make it easy to tell apart,

1161
00:36:38,520 --> 00:36:39,640
I made some tags.

1162
00:36:39,640 --> 00:36:40,560
You can check them out yourselves.

1163
00:36:41,040 --> 00:36:41,320
Alright.

1164
00:36:41,640 --> 00:36:42,400
Let's go back.

1165
00:36:42,400 --> 00:36:43,040
Let's go.

1166
00:36:43,040 --> 00:36:44,720
(Truth Inn)

1167
00:36:44,720 --> 00:36:48,160
Everyone, come with me

1168
00:36:48,160 --> 00:36:50,040
and head into the room for a discussion.

1169
00:36:50,040 --> 00:36:50,640
Sounds good.

1170
00:36:50,640 --> 00:36:52,560
Look at him acting all smug.

1171
00:36:52,560 --> 00:36:55,560
Jiawei is really playing
the Alpha CEO type today.

1172
00:36:55,580 --> 00:36:56,760
(Detective's Alpha CEO moment)

1173
00:36:56,760 --> 00:36:58,320
We got three clues.

1174
00:36:58,320 --> 00:37:01,000
Let's see just how innocent
you guys really are.

1175
00:37:06,080 --> 00:37:07,560
Come on. Let's see what's in Ding's.

1176
00:37:07,560 --> 00:37:08,780
(Ding)

1177
00:37:16,720 --> 00:37:18,640
Why is there

1178
00:37:18,640 --> 00:37:20,120
a doll of me in here?

1179
00:37:20,120 --> 00:37:22,200
And there are words written on the back.

1180
00:37:22,200 --> 00:37:24,200
Shameless scoundrel.
What's that supposed to mean?

1181
00:37:24,200 --> 00:37:24,500
(Ning Waver)

1182
00:37:24,620 --> 00:37:26,260
(Shameless scoundrel)

1183
00:37:27,240 --> 00:37:28,240
Ning Waver.

1184
00:37:29,560 --> 00:37:30,880
You're utterly shameless.

1185
00:37:36,720 --> 00:37:37,880
Ning Waver.

1186
00:37:37,880 --> 00:37:40,300
(Utterly shameless)
You're utterly shameless.

1187
00:37:40,300 --> 00:37:41,540
(Cunning crook)
A cunning crook.

1188
00:37:46,340 --> 00:37:47,540
(Lapdog)

1189
00:37:47,540 --> 00:37:49,620
(Utterly shameless)

1190
00:37:49,620 --> 00:37:51,380
(Cunning crook)

1191
00:37:52,400 --> 00:37:53,160
Are you talking about me?

1192
00:37:53,680 --> 00:37:54,080
Yes, you.

1193
00:37:54,340 --> 00:37:55,180
(Blank memory)

1194
00:37:57,100 --> 00:37:57,700
(Utterly shameless, Cunning crook)

1195
00:37:57,720 --> 00:37:59,920
(Ning Waver's memory loading 20%)
What did I even do?

1196
00:38:00,560 --> 00:38:01,600
Let me break it down slowly.

1197
00:38:02,040 --> 00:38:03,280
This is

1198
00:38:03,280 --> 00:38:06,480
the latest martial arts masters
leaderboard for Year 255 of Tui.

1199
00:38:06,580 --> 00:38:07,480
(Latest Martial Arts Masters Leaderboard)

1200
00:38:07,480 --> 00:38:08,280
First place,

1201
00:38:08,280 --> 00:38:10,280
General Dong, the grand general
of the Longdong army.

1202
00:38:10,280 --> 00:38:13,440
Second place, Shi Damen,
the leader of Shi Damen Sect.

1203
00:38:13,440 --> 00:38:16,000
Third place, Lord Tui of Chivalry Manor.

1204
00:38:16,000 --> 00:38:16,840
The weapons leaderboard.

1205
00:38:16,840 --> 00:38:18,320
Longdong Spear,
the ultimate spear in the world.

1206
00:38:18,320 --> 00:38:20,080
Qide Sword, the ultimate sword
in the world.

1207
00:38:20,080 --> 00:38:22,080
Wounds inflicted by it

1208
00:38:22,080 --> 00:38:23,760
will show silver marks.

1209
00:38:23,760 --> 00:38:24,940
(Qide Sword,
the ultimate sword in the world)

1210
00:38:24,940 --> 00:38:26,660
(Wounds inflicted by it
will show silver marks)

1211
00:38:26,680 --> 00:38:28,240
I drew Lord Tui.

1212
00:38:28,240 --> 00:38:31,520
And then next to him, I drew
him kneeling beside Longdong Spear.

1213
00:38:31,520 --> 00:38:32,540
(Lord Tui)

1214
00:38:33,160 --> 00:38:33,640
Why?

1215
00:38:34,040 --> 00:38:36,360
Because he's a wolf in sheep's clothing.

1216
00:38:38,920 --> 00:38:40,720
Lately, I've been tailing Ning Waver.

1217
00:38:41,600 --> 00:38:42,360
One day,

1218
00:38:42,360 --> 00:38:43,680
I was eavesdropping at the door.

1219
00:38:43,680 --> 00:38:44,680
Lord Tui said,

1220
00:38:45,560 --> 00:38:46,760
"Lately,"

1221
00:38:46,760 --> 00:38:48,240
"there are still people defying me."

1222
00:38:48,240 --> 00:38:49,320
"Kill them."

1223
00:38:49,700 --> 00:38:50,800
(Lord Tui orders Ning Waver
to kill those who defy him?)

1224
00:38:50,800 --> 00:38:52,920
In my mind, Lord Tui's image

1225
00:38:52,920 --> 00:38:54,680
was always that of a hero,

1226
00:38:54,680 --> 00:38:55,760
a good guy who helps the poor.

1227
00:38:55,760 --> 00:38:58,160
Who knew that the philanthropist

1228
00:38:58,160 --> 00:38:59,760
was actually a wolf?

1229
00:39:02,640 --> 00:39:05,480
A martial arts treasure
like Longdong Spear

1230
00:39:05,480 --> 00:39:07,400
is actually in the hands
of such a cunning crook.

1231
00:39:07,880 --> 00:39:08,760
I'm not happy about it.

1232
00:39:09,040 --> 00:39:09,520
Wait.

1233
00:39:10,000 --> 00:39:11,440
Why are you so unhappy

1234
00:39:11,440 --> 00:39:12,920
that Longdong Spear is in his hands?

1235
00:39:12,920 --> 00:39:13,960
What's your connection...

1236
00:39:14,480 --> 00:39:17,000
Because my mentor always taught me...

1237
00:39:17,600 --> 00:39:18,240
Hold this for a second.

1238
00:39:22,620 --> 00:39:24,830
(Chivalry comes first)

1239
00:39:24,830 --> 00:39:26,800
(Chivalry speaks for the people)

1240
00:39:26,800 --> 00:39:28,480
Ding, your path of chivalry

1241
00:39:28,480 --> 00:39:29,760
is for you to find on your own.

1242
00:39:29,760 --> 00:39:33,540
(Passionate Youth Ding!)

1243
00:39:33,660 --> 00:39:36,420
(That's so epic!)

1244
00:39:37,200 --> 00:39:38,200
Is your mentor still alive?

1245
00:39:38,680 --> 00:39:39,200
Alright.

1246
00:39:39,640 --> 00:39:40,160
Here we go.

1247
00:39:40,520 --> 00:39:41,880
It's this comic book, right?

1248
00:39:41,880 --> 00:39:43,080
Yeah, it's this comic book.

1249
00:39:44,060 --> 00:39:46,140
(Tears flow before words can come)

1250
00:39:51,640 --> 00:39:52,200
A crying scene.

1251
00:39:52,200 --> 00:39:52,720
An emotional scene.

1252
00:39:52,720 --> 00:39:53,760
Everyone, give him...

1253
00:39:54,000 --> 00:39:54,840
Give him some time.

1254
00:39:55,600 --> 00:39:56,480
If you can't cry today,

1255
00:39:56,480 --> 00:39:57,520
we'll sit here and cry with you.

1256
00:39:57,540 --> 00:39:58,980
(Let you cry your eyes out)

1257
00:39:59,020 --> 00:40:00,580
(Wait till I become the detective!)

1258
00:40:00,760 --> 00:40:02,560
We need to clear the room.

1259
00:40:04,120 --> 00:40:05,200
This comic book,

1260
00:40:05,800 --> 00:40:06,960
as you can see...

1261
00:40:07,500 --> 00:40:08,980
(Let me see)

1262
00:40:09,000 --> 00:40:10,680
There's someone wearing a cloak

1263
00:40:11,360 --> 00:40:13,080
and a hat teaching me
how to swing a sword.

1264
00:40:13,080 --> 00:40:13,960
This is me,

1265
00:40:13,960 --> 00:40:15,080
and this is my mentor.

1266
00:40:15,360 --> 00:40:17,920
Back then I was just
a self-taught, rogue amateur fighter.

1267
00:40:18,280 --> 00:40:18,840
My mentor

1268
00:40:18,840 --> 00:40:21,160
suddenly showed up a year ago
and taught me martial arts.

1269
00:40:21,160 --> 00:40:22,840
He always showed up at night,

1270
00:40:23,320 --> 00:40:25,080
and then by the time the sun came up,

1271
00:40:25,080 --> 00:40:26,240
he'd suddenly vanish.

1272
00:40:28,760 --> 00:40:29,320
To me,

1273
00:40:29,320 --> 00:40:31,280
he was like my

1274
00:40:31,280 --> 00:40:32,000
father.

1275
00:40:32,200 --> 00:40:33,560
(Ding Pillar sees his mentor as his father)
Yeah, my father.

1276
00:40:33,880 --> 00:40:35,520
Since he always showed up at night,

1277
00:40:35,520 --> 00:40:37,680
I called him Uncle Dream.

1278
00:40:37,680 --> 00:40:38,600
His flask broke,

1279
00:40:38,600 --> 00:40:40,520
so I even made him a new one

1280
00:40:40,520 --> 00:40:42,120
and carved the word "Dream" on it.

1281
00:40:42,120 --> 00:40:43,760
And what's this stuff on here?

1282
00:40:43,760 --> 00:40:45,360
And why is this here?

1283
00:40:46,160 --> 00:40:47,120
No value.

1284
00:40:47,120 --> 00:40:48,280
You can die now.

1285
00:40:49,200 --> 00:40:50,600
I tailed you this whole time.

1286
00:40:50,600 --> 00:40:52,720
I stumbled upon this by accident.

1287
00:40:52,720 --> 00:40:54,680
It's my mentor's jade pendant.

1288
00:40:55,400 --> 00:40:57,120
(Chivalry, Ding Pillar's mentor)
He always kept this pendant on him.

1289
00:40:57,120 --> 00:40:58,360
(Uncle Dream's jade pendant)
Where the jade goes, he goes.

1290
00:40:58,360 --> 00:41:00,080
And it's covered in blood.

1291
00:41:00,080 --> 00:41:01,720
Written next to it is "No value".

1292
00:41:01,720 --> 00:41:03,040
"You can die now".

1293
00:41:03,040 --> 00:41:04,520
(No value. You can die now.)

1294
00:41:04,520 --> 00:41:05,680
So I figured you must have

1295
00:41:05,680 --> 00:41:07,160
killed my mentor.

1296
00:41:07,260 --> 00:41:10,980
(Ding Pillar's master
was killed by Ning Waver)

1297
00:41:11,000 --> 00:41:12,280
Then I wrote beside it,

1298
00:41:12,280 --> 00:41:13,720
The one who should "die" is you.

1299
00:41:13,720 --> 00:41:14,960
Ning Waver.

1300
00:41:14,960 --> 00:41:15,540
(Ning Waver identity info breakdown)

1301
00:41:15,540 --> 00:41:16,280
(Relevant person: Ding Pillar.
Impression of Ning: shameless jerk)

1302
00:41:16,290 --> 00:41:16,960
(Incident related to Ning:
Ning killed Uncle Dream)

1303
00:41:16,970 --> 00:41:18,200
Ning Waver

1304
00:41:18,200 --> 00:41:21,160
keeps randomly beating
me up every few days.

1305
00:41:21,300 --> 00:41:22,940
(Ning Waver beats
Ding Pillar for no reason)

1306
00:41:22,960 --> 00:41:24,080
It's him.

1307
00:41:24,400 --> 00:41:25,520
You petty jerk!

1308
00:41:25,880 --> 00:41:26,920
What?

1309
00:41:28,520 --> 00:41:30,000
You're so big and tall,

1310
00:41:30,000 --> 00:41:31,720
but you're actually a petty little man!

1311
00:41:31,720 --> 00:41:33,160
From the very beginning,

1312
00:41:33,160 --> 00:41:34,240
I did all this

1313
00:41:34,240 --> 00:41:35,360
because of Ning Waver.

1314
00:41:35,360 --> 00:41:37,320
I didn't know why he kept hitting me.

1315
00:41:38,520 --> 00:41:40,360
Don't you think you're too handsome?

1316
00:41:40,460 --> 00:41:42,000
(Can't argue with that)

1317
00:41:42,000 --> 00:41:43,400
You need to look at yourself.

1318
00:41:43,400 --> 00:41:44,880
You say he's handsome.

1319
00:41:45,160 --> 00:41:46,200
Aren't you handsome too?

1320
00:41:46,200 --> 00:41:47,160
I am.

1321
00:41:47,160 --> 00:41:48,160
(Blurted out: handsome)

1322
00:41:48,160 --> 00:41:49,800
(No, wait)
I also deserve a beating.

1323
00:41:52,480 --> 00:41:55,120
We're both the kind of handsome
that makes people wanna hit us.

1324
00:41:55,120 --> 00:41:57,000
But I'm good at martial arts.

1325
00:41:58,560 --> 00:42:01,840
So I made this little gauze doll.

1326
00:42:01,840 --> 00:42:04,280
I can't beat him, so I can only beat it.

1327
00:42:07,240 --> 00:42:09,880
Does your master have the Qide Sword?

1328
00:42:12,680 --> 00:42:13,480
I don't know.

1329
00:42:14,240 --> 00:42:16,640
I think there's another point
everyone may have missed.

1330
00:42:16,640 --> 00:42:17,200
What?

1331
00:42:17,200 --> 00:42:18,720
Yesterday, I saw

1332
00:42:18,720 --> 00:42:21,200
the man in black carrying him
after he'd been knocked out.

1333
00:42:21,200 --> 00:42:24,360
They were carrying him
toward Chivalry Manor.

1334
00:42:25,080 --> 00:42:26,000
The Qide Sword?

1335
00:42:26,400 --> 00:42:27,440
Don't hurt my son!

1336
00:42:28,120 --> 00:42:29,760
Let's think from the killer's side.

1337
00:42:30,040 --> 00:42:32,240
If I went to fight someone,

1338
00:42:32,240 --> 00:42:34,440
and I knocked out the guy
I wanted to knock out,

1339
00:42:34,440 --> 00:42:36,200
why would I still carry him

1340
00:42:36,200 --> 00:42:37,640
to Chivalry Manor?

1341
00:42:38,040 --> 00:42:38,440
It must be because

1342
00:42:38,440 --> 00:42:40,840
there's something I want
inside Chivalry Manor.

1343
00:42:42,080 --> 00:42:43,800
Or an answer I'm looking for.

1344
00:42:45,240 --> 00:42:45,800
Yes.

1345
00:42:46,400 --> 00:42:47,240
On Ding.

1346
00:42:47,240 --> 00:42:48,440
I think that's the point.

1347
00:42:48,840 --> 00:42:50,200
He wants the Longdong Spear.

1348
00:42:50,220 --> 00:42:50,690
(Ding Pillar's motive for murder)

1349
00:42:50,690 --> 00:42:51,160
(Toward Ning Waver: beaten
for no reason)

1350
00:42:51,160 --> 00:42:51,720
(Suspects Ning killed his master
and wants revenge)

1351
00:42:51,720 --> 00:42:52,290
(Toward Lord Tui:
discovered his hidden crimes)

1352
00:42:52,290 --> 00:42:52,790
(He doesn't deserve the spear,
so Ding wants it)

1353
00:42:52,810 --> 00:42:53,300
(With both weapons,
one can rule the world)

1354
00:42:53,320 --> 00:42:54,280
What did you call me just now?

1355
00:42:54,280 --> 00:42:55,040
A lapdog?

1356
00:42:55,040 --> 00:42:55,520
Right.

1357
00:42:55,520 --> 00:42:57,440
And this says I'm shameless.

1358
00:42:57,440 --> 00:42:57,920
Fine.

1359
00:42:57,920 --> 00:43:00,400
Let's see what else people
are calling me today.

1360
00:43:00,400 --> 00:43:00,800
Come on!

1361
00:43:01,120 --> 00:43:01,320
Okay.

1362
00:43:01,320 --> 00:43:02,920
